{"tid":2163793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"私人教育機構（收月費）八號波唔補堂","createTime":"2020-08-19T00:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T01:12:27.000Z","uid":207316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63d6bf8599cd416d62240034cf79ab3f43f0dca2","tid":2163793,"uid":207316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我報左個超貴課程，<br />\n關於某啲技巧治療，<br />\n收月費12,600，每日2小時，已上兩個幾月<br />\n屬私人教育機構，有時多野問加鐘同加訓練要比成1200一粒鐘，半粒鐘650（月費外逐鐘比）<br />\n多一分鐘都計你數<br />\n<br />\n今朝八號波打去問有冇得上<br />\n佢哋話暫停，<br />\n問有冇補堂話冇<br />\n但扣一日計番都成600<br />\n佢哋竟然話冇補堂，錢照計<br />\n<br />\n我心諗平時計到咁盡，<br />\n私人教育機構真係好吸血<br />\n<br />\n呻下，聽日繼續番學"},{"pid":"5d3d8c4a74a151054dbfe969668c286795d41c44","tid":2163793,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:04:10.000Z","msg":"教咩?"},{"pid":"e44b1ed83a679c3fecc91342c3d29ba0996f54ee","tid":2163793,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"有無牌都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd53f73d58649cf3a26d6c160bd97fbd18c817f5","tid":2163793,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e44b1ed83a679c3fecc91342c3d29ba0996f54ee","tid":2163793,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"有無牌都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"唔係樣樣野都要拎牌既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f4f3ac85646fcb3e50b8506e0b96e95b56bcb8","tid":2163793,"uid":207316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44b1ed83a679c3fecc91342c3d29ba0996f54ee","tid":2163793,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"有無牌都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sm